  "text": "We selected the case of how the Port Authority of New York and New Jersey has responded to the issue of homelessness because of the issue's social relevance and its visibility to both organization members and outside constituencies. In this sense, the case meets the criteria for an \"extreme case,\" one in which the process of theoretical interest is more transparent than it would be in other cases [CITATION_1] .",
